  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO REQUIRE A FOREIGN THIRD-PARTY LITIGATION FUNDER TO DISCLOSE CERTAIN INFORMATION TO THE ATTORNEY GENERAL; TO REQUIRE SUCH DISCLOSURE IN WRITING TO THE ATTORNEY GENERAL; TO REQUIRE  THE DISCLOSURE NO MORE THAN 30 DAYS AFTER EXECUTION OF THE AGREEMENT; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
